Products
1. Get All Products
Method: GET
Endpoint: /products

Query Params
Name	Type	Description
page	number	Page number
limit	number	Number of items per page
minPrice	number	Minimum price
maxPrice	number	Maximum price
sort	string	Sort field/order
Example Success Response
{    "success": true,    "data": [        {            "id": "product_id",            "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",            "price": 1299.99,            "stock": 25,            "images": [        }    ],    "pagination": {        "page": 1,        "limit": 10,        "total": 1,                "https://cdn.example.                    com/product.jpg"            ]        "pages": 1    }}
